This project presents a end-to-end data analytics solution for Bright Coffee Shop,
developed as part of a Junior Data Analyst assessment. The objective is to analyze 
daily transactional sales data and deliver actionable insights to support the CEO 
in making informed business decisions around revenue growth and product performance.

Objectives
- Identify which products generate the most revenue
- Determine peak sales time intervals throughout the day
- Analyze sales trends across products and time buckets
- Provide data-driven recommendations to improve sales performance
